only diff is that we have added some animation effect in it

-webkit-animation: fadeEffect 1s;
animation: fadeEffect 1s;

in tab-content class

and added css animation rules as follows
@-webkit-keyframes fadeEffect{
    from{opacity: 0;}
    to{opacity: 1;}
}
@keyframes fadeEffect{
    from{opacity: 0;}
    to{opacity: 1;}
}